interpretation:
The "woman standing" card represents stability, independence, and a sense of being grounded. The woman in this card is firmly planted on the ground, symbolizing a strong foundation and a sense of balance. She embodies self-confidence and a steadfast determination to stand her ground. This card can indicate that you have a solid footing in your current situation and are able to handle any challenges that come your way. It also suggests that you are independent and capable of making your own decisions.

Overall, the "woman standing" card encourages you to stand firm in your convictions and to trust in your abilities. It is a reminder that you have the strength and resilience to overcome any obstacles and to achieve your goals.
